snippet.title: Hyderabad GHMC Election: CM Yogi को लेकर क्या बोले हैदराबाद वाले?
snippet.description:
देश के सबसे बड़े नगर निगम में से एक ग्रेटर हैदराबाद नगर निगम के चुनाव में बीजेपी ने जबरदस्त प्रदर्शन करते हुए 49 सीटों पर जीत हासिल की है. वहीं, केसीआर की पार्टी टीआरएस को 56 और असदुद्दीन ओवैसी की पार्टी AIMIM को 43 सीटों पर जीत मिली. हालांकि, इस बार किसी भी पार्टी को बहुमत नहीं मिला है. 150 वार्डों वाले ग्रेटर हैदराबाद नगर निगम में बहुमत का आंकड़ा 75 है..

snippet.title: Clash Royale: NEW LEGENDARY CARD REVEAL 😮 TV Royale Update
snippet.description:
https://www.youtube.com/esportsroyale
☝️☝️☝️ WATCH THE CLASH ROYALE WORLD FINALS HERE ☝️☝️☝️

It's our first Legendary card since the Fisherman entered the Arena in July 2019! Find out who she is and catch up on what's coming in the next Clash Royale Season... LOGMAS.

Follow Drew & Brice: https://twitter.com/drewbian & https://www.instagram.com/bricelavillesaintmartin_3d/

Subscribe for more! ►► http://supr.cl/SubRoyale

Enter the Arena! From the creators of Clash of Clans comes a real-time multiplayer game starring the Royales, your favorite Clash characters and much, much more.

Collect and upgrade dozens of cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defenses you know and love, as well as the Royales: Princes, Knights, Baby Dragons and more. Knock the enemy King and Princesses from their towers to defeat your opponents and win Trophies, Crowns and glory in the Arena. Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community.

Lead the Clash Royale Family to victory!

FEATURES
• Duel players from around the world in real-time in both 1v1 and 2v2 Battles
• Earn chests to unlock rewards, collect powerful new cards and upgrade existing ones
• Destroy opponent's towers and win Crowns to earn epic Crown chests
• Build and upgrade your card collection with the Clash Royale Family along with dozens of your favorite Clash troops, spells and defenses
• Construct your ultimate Battle Deck to defeat your opponents
• Progress through multiple Arenas all the way to the top
• Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community
• Challenge your Clanmates and friends to a private duel, or play side-by-side in a 2v2 Battle
• Work together with your Clan to unlock Clan Chests
• Play new events every week
• Learn different battle tactics by watching the best duels on TV Royale

PLEASE NOTE! Clash Royale is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash Royale. A network connection is also required.

Support:
Are you having problems? Visit http://supercell.helpshift.com/a/clash-royale/ or contact us in-game by going to Settings, Help and support.

Privacy Policy:
http://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

snippet.description:
Los Angeles rapper Ohgeesy, debuts his first solo single “Bandemic” via his Youtube and Soundcloud platforms. 

The Ace The Face produced track is being released alongside a EDD themed merchandise drop. The drop includes a variety of T-shirts and hoodies that can be purchased exclusively on Ohgeesy’s website geezyworld.com 

Ohgeesy’s first solo project GEEZY WORLD is set to be released early next year.

snippet.title: The Mandalorian Season 2 Episode 6 Breakdown OH MY GOD
snippet.description:
This episode had it all! The Mandalorian Season 2 Episode 6 finally shows the one and only, Boba Fett in the spotlight. We see Boba return and eventually help Din Djarin and Grogu against Moff Gideon's Storm Troopers and Dark Troopers (phase 2 I think), who end up taking Grogu.
Fennec Shand reminds me a lot of Zam Wessel from Attack of the Clones, who was pursued by Anakin Skywalker and Obi-Wan Kenobi, until Jango showed up.

We also learn a lot about Jango Fett, Boba Fett's Father. We learn that Jango Fett was a Mandalorian! This is awesome! Since it was skewed in canon, it's nice to know we finally have an answer. They seem to be following his story from Open Seasons comic book series which shows the story of Jango as a boy. Long story short, Jango was the son of a farmer on Concord Dawn. A man named Jaster Mereel who was leader of the True Mandalorians, was on the run from a traitor named Tor Vizsla from Death Watch. Jango’s dad hid Jaster Mereel in his farm, and told Jango that he was feeding some homeless men. When Tor Vizsla came looking near Jango’s Dad’s farm, he found Jango’s Dad and beat him up infant of Jango, until Jango’s mom created a distraction and Jango ran for his life, leaving his parents who were immediately murdered, Fett ran into Jaster Mereel who eventually took the boy under his wing and recruited him in the Mandalorian Civil War against Death Watch, as one of the True Mandalorians. Jaster died eventually and Jango avenged him, becoming the leader of the True Mandalorians. Now the people who found Din, were death watch, so the two clans have always been waging wars against one another and have varying beliefs. 

Explaining this to Din, Din accepts that the armour belongs to Boba. So this armour, is just repainted from his dad’s, from Jango’s. The deal is done, says Din, where Boba assures him that it is not, as he promised the safety of the child in return for his armour. Now Boba joins the crew until the child is safe. Flying in the Slave 1, they arrive on Nevarro 7, where Cara Dune is now a New Republic Marshal, where he asks her to locate Mayfeld, who you might remember from season 1. Mando is going to spring him out of jail to locate Moff Gideon’s cruiser.

We jump to Moff Gideon’s light cruiser, he walks to the cell containing the child.

As Moff Gideon enters, we see Grogu using the force on stormtroopers. Even going as far as using force choke, to which many might think is a dark side move, but, I should mention, Luke Skywalker used it as well in Return of the Jedi, and he was far from the dark side.

As Grogu knocks them out, Gideon steps up to him and ignites his 
dark saber, asking Grogu if he remembers one of these, meaning if he remembers using a lightsaber or having seen many lightsabers during his time as a Jedi at the Jedi Temple before Order 66. Grogu is tired, I think because he had to cut himself off from the force for so long that he isn’t used to using it as much as when he was at the Jedi temple learning from the many masters. Using the force can also tire one out, like it does to Luke in the empire strikes back when failing to lift the x-wing out of Yoda’s swamp. They blast Grogu with a stun blast, and cuff him. Gideon tells his officer to contact Dr. Pershing, the cloning doctor responsible for the experiments on the child, to tell him that they have their donor. The plan now is for Gideon to kill Grogu to harvest all of his blood which has force powers, or in Star Wars lingo, a high Midichlorian count. End of the episode.

It was amazing. Simply amazing. My favourite episode of the entire show so far, which is saying a lot. Boba is back and badder than ever, as Terry Silver would say. I think the next episode will revolve around rescuing Mayfeld from Jail, and then tracking the light cruiser or going to Dr. Pershing who will have the child momentarily. I think the season finale will end in a Big Bang all out battle like end game. With everyone we’ve seen from this season fighting together against Moff Gideon and his dark troopers, as he himself gets in a phase 3 dark trooper mega suit to destroy Din. Hopefully Ahsoka Tano returns with Bo Katan, and we get to see another Jedi, Luke or Ezra is my guess.

snippet.title: Dua Lipa: Tiny Desk (Home) Concert
snippet.description:
The Tiny Desk is working from home for the foreseeable future. Introducing NPR Music's Tiny Desk (home) concerts, bringing you performances from across the country and the world. It's the same spirit — stripped-down sets, an intimate setting — just a different space.

Dec. 4, 2020 | Abby O'Neill -- With a genuine smile stretched across her face, Dua Lipa seems overjoyed to reconnect with her band for their only performance since their tour in support of her sophomore album, Future Nostalgia, was cancelled in March. Glowing from the inside out and accentuated by the apricot hues of a backdrop in a London studio, Dua and her backup vocalists and band bring life and warmth into households in need of "levitating" and some pep in their step this winter. This vibrant four song set of dance hits, all from Future Nostalgia, will surely have you cutting up the floor in your kitchen while quarantining in the cold weather.

While we can't film our Tiny Desk concerts at NPR's D.C. office during the pandemic, our "home" series has created opportunity for global megastars like Dua Lipa to bring her uptempo dance joints all the way from London. Of Kosovar Albanian descent, Dua Lipa was raised in the UK and rose to super stardom in the three years since her eponymous debut album dropped in 2017. NPR Music featured her in our docu-series Noteworthy at the onset of her career. It's been extraordinary to witness her colossal takeover of the pop music landscape. Dua sums the times during her intro of "Love Again": "It's about manifesting good things into your life, when things aren't quite going your way."

SET LIST
"Levitating"
"Pretty Please"
"Love Again"
"Don't Start Now"

MUSICIANS
Dua Lipa: vocals
Matthew Carroll: bass
Alex Lanyon: guitar
Naomi Scarlett: vocals
Ciara O'Connor: vocals
Izzy Chase: vocals
Matthew Allen: vocals

CREDITS
Video: Ceremony London, James Barnes
Audio: WFB Live, Will Nicholson
TINY DESK TEAM
Producer: Abby O'Neill
Video Producer: Morgan Noelle Smith
Audio Mastering: Josh Rogosin
Associate Producer
Tiny Production Team: Bob Boilen, Kara Frame, Maia Stern
Executive Producer: Lauren Onkey
Senior VP, Programming: Anya Grundmann

With Warner Bros. recently announcing that their entire 2021 slate will premiere on HBO Max as well as theaters on the same day, "the death of cinema" is once again a topic of discussion. Let's talk about the benefits and drawbacks of what could be on the horizon.

snippet.title: Soft & Crispy Focaccia | Claire Saffitz | Dessert Person
snippet.description:
Watch Claire Saffitz make soft & crispy focaccia, a recipe from her cookbook, Dessert Person. Not only is the recipe forgiving, making it a great introduction to breadmaking for novice bakers, it's incredibly versatile and serves as the perfect accompaniment to any meal (hello, soup weather!). You might be surprised to see just how easy it is to make a tall, fluffy, light focaccia.

#ClaireSaffitz #DessertPerson #Focaccia

Special Equipment:
Instant-read thermometer
Stand mixer
Scale
Standard half-sheet pan (18x13 inches)

Ingredients:
1 (1/4 oz / 7g) envelope active dry yeast
6 cups bread flour (24oz / 780g)
2 tablespoons Diamond Crystal kosher salt (0.6oz / 17g)
1/2 cup extra-virgin olive oil (5oz / 110g), plus 1/4 cup for topping plain focaccia and more for oiling hands
Optional toppings
Flaky salt, for sprinkling the top

Video Breakdown:
0:00 Start
0:15 Intro to Focaccia
0:43 Show Intro / Animation
1:00 Dessert Person
2:00 Ingredients/Special Equipment
3:20 Mix The Dough
4:57 First Rise
6:09 Fold & Proof
8:13 Prepare Toppings
10:10 Dimpling & Baking
13:59 Taste Test / Outro

snippet.title: Why are Billions of Dollars Worth of Ships Being Intentionally Destroyed?
snippet.description:
This video was made possible by our Patreon community! ❤️
See new videos early, participate in exclusive Q&As, and more!
➡️ https://www.patreon.com/EconomicsExplained

▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀

This is the Carnival Imagination, a luxury cruise liner worth hundreds of millions of dollars, which just 10 short months ago was touring passengers in extreme comfort to exotic destinations all over the world. 

This ship is sailing dead ahead to its final port of call, where it has been sold for scrap alongside dozens of other ships that have become the latest victims of the global pandemic. 

The Chittagong ship breaking yard in Bangladesh is the largest of its kind in the world, and in the past few months even its abundant shores have become inundated with pleasure cruises and industrial cargo ships alike that all could have otherwise sailed the oceans for many more decades. 

These are all very troubling signs for the unsung heroes of our modern global economy, the merchant marine fleet. Every year trillions of dollars worth of cargo is transported on ships like these and losing this fleet could turn into a huge barrier to global trade.

But what is really going on here?

Why would profit-motivated companies destroy billions of dollars worth of productive assets? Sure times are tough, tourism and trade have declined massively but this hardly looks like a reasonable response right?

I don’t burn down my house if a video gets less than 10,000 likes, so why would companies in such a competitive industry do something equally as self-destructive?

Well as always it has to do with economics (go figure) and to understand this bizarre behavior we need to understand a few key areas.

What are the economics behind the merchant marine fleet?

How do these factors make it financially viable to destroy ships?

what does this mean for the future of international trade?

And what does this all have to do with Chinese bridge building?

snippet.title: Dua Lipa: Tiny Desk (Home) Concert
snippet.description:
The Tiny Desk is working from home for the foreseeable future. Introducing NPR Music's Tiny Desk (home) concerts, bringing you performances from across the country and the world. It's the same spirit — stripped-down sets, an intimate setting — just a different space.

Dec. 4, 2020 | Abby O'Neill -- With a genuine smile stretched across her face, Dua Lipa seems overjoyed to reconnect with her band for their only performance since their tour in support of her sophomore album, Future Nostalgia, was cancelled in March. Glowing from the inside out and accentuated by the apricot hues of a backdrop in a London studio, Dua and her backup vocalists and band bring life and warmth into households in need of "levitating" and some pep in their step this winter. This vibrant four song set of dance hits, all from Future Nostalgia, will surely have you cutting up the floor in your kitchen while quarantining in the cold weather.

While we can't film our Tiny Desk concerts at NPR's D.C. office during the pandemic, our "home" series has created opportunity for global megastars like Dua Lipa to bring her uptempo dance joints all the way from London. Of Kosovar Albanian descent, Dua Lipa was raised in the UK and rose to super stardom in the three years since her eponymous debut album dropped in 2017. NPR Music featured her in our docu-series Noteworthy at the onset of her career. It's been extraordinary to witness her colossal takeover of the pop music landscape. Dua sums the times during her intro of "Love Again": "It's about manifesting good things into your life, when things aren't quite going your way."

SET LIST
"Levitating"
"Pretty Please"
"Love Again"
"Don't Start Now"

MUSICIANS
Dua Lipa: vocals
Matthew Carroll: bass
Alex Lanyon: guitar
Naomi Scarlett: vocals
Ciara O'Connor: vocals
Izzy Chase: vocals
Matthew Allen: vocals

CREDITS
Video: Ceremony London, James Barnes
Audio: WFB Live, Will Nicholson
TINY DESK TEAM
Producer: Abby O'Neill
Video Producer: Morgan Noelle Smith
Audio Mastering: Josh Rogosin
Associate Producer
Tiny Production Team: Bob Boilen, Kara Frame, Maia Stern
Executive Producer: Lauren Onkey
Senior VP, Programming: Anya Grundmann

احصل على FIFA 21 على أي من PlayStation 4 أو Xbox One قبل إصدار FIFA 22 , وقم بترقية لعبتك على منصة الجيل القادم المماثلة (PlayStation 5 أو Xbox Series X|S) مجاناً. سيتم ترحيل كل التقدم الذي حققته والمحتوى الذي حصلت عليه في FIFA 21 Ultimate Team و VOLTA FOOTBALL! التفاصيل الكاملة: http://x.ea.com/66708

العب FIFA 21 قبل 15 يناير 2021 وبداءً من 15 ديسمبر*, ستستلم عنصراً ليس للمقايضة من David Beckham في FUT, وستحصل عليه كمبتكر في VOLTA! http://x.ea.com/66710

احصل على FIFA 21 الآن! http://x.ea.com/66709

اشترك لمشاهدة المزيد من مقاطع فيديو FIFA 21: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD.

"The Blinding"
غناء Jay Electronica

#FIFA21 #FeelNextLevel
localizations.fi.title: FIFA 21 | Next Gen -julkaisutraileri (PS5 ja Xbox Series X|S) [4K]
localizations.fi.description:
Tunne seuraava taso FIFA 21 -pelissä PlayStation 5- ja Xbox Series X-|S -konsoleille nyt uusilla teknologioilla, joita ovat esimerkiksi salamannopeat latausajat, EA SPORTS GameCam™ ja LiveLight-hahmonnus, joka vie koko maailman pelin visuaalisesta vaistomaiseksi: http://x.ea.com/66707

Hanki oikeutus FIFA 21 -peliin PlayStation 4-järjestelmällä tai Xbox Onella ennen FIFA 22 -pelin julkaisemista ja päivitä pelisi vastaavaksi seuraavan sukupolven konsolin versioksi (PlayStation 5 tai Xbox Series X|S) ilmaiseksi. Kaikki FIFA 21 Ultimate Team- ja VOLTA FOOTBALL -tiloissa saavuttamasi edistyminen ja hankkimasi sisältö siirtyvät uuteen versioon! Kaikki tiedot: http://x.ea.com/66708

Pelaa FIFA 21 -peliä 15. tammikuuta 2021 mennessä, niin saat 15. joulukuuta alkaen FUT-tilassa David Beckham -kortin, jolla ei voi käydä kauppaa, ja saat hänet VOLTA Groundbreakerina! http://x.ea.com/66710

Hanki FIFA 21 nyt! http://x.ea.com/66709

Tilaa nähdäksesi lisää FIFA 21 -videoita: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD.

”The Blinding”
Esittäjä Jay Electronica

#FIFA21 #FeelNextLevel

Why do all the monsters come out at night?
why do we sleep where we want to hide?
why do I run back to you like I don't mind if you fuck up my life?

snippet.title: The Pengest Munch Ep. 31: Chester's (Ilford)
snippet.description:
This week I went East for my wing excursion and it was not worth the bop. It was a case of catfish; the exterior decor lures you in, then the interior decor continues to gas you, then you cop a meal and realize expeditiously it was all a facade 🤦🏾‍♂️ It's a very nice facade though, great to look at and shoot in, but food is the last thing people should be rolling here for 😄

snippet.title: Dear Nia
snippet.description:
This is not a good summation of the many-worlds interpretation of quantum mechanics. This is what happens when you stay up reading about it while imbibing moderate-to-inadvisable amounts of beer. (I’m sure Nia and Soren were fine in the end. (More stuff below.))

 For a considerably better summation of the many-worlds interpretation of quantum mechanics: https://youtu.be/kxvQ3Wyw2M4 

Discord server ► https://discord.gg/76ybBSR 
The Fifth Science Paperback ► https://tinyurl.com/y5zj33s5 (you may need to change your region accordingly: .co.uk, etc) 
T-shirts, mugs, and sadness ► https://teespring.com/stores/exurb1a 
The rest of my books ► https://tinyurl.com/ycnl5bo3 
I also make horrendous music ► https://soundcloud.com/exurbia-1 
For sending personalised insults ► https://www.facebook.com/exurb1a/ 
Help me to do this full-time if you're deranged enough ► https://www.patreon.com/exurb1r?ty=h 

The music used ► Karma – Patrick Mottram https://youtu.be/EbvOWk2on5M 

A little note about where I’ve been: I’m not dead, unless you mean spiritually. I’m trying my hardest to finish the new book and it takes up most of my time and allotted crying episodes. I’ll do my best to return to something bordering on a ‘normal’ upload schedule when it’s finally finished and out, promise. Hope you’re doing well :)

snippet.title: Hear U Out 权听你说 EP26 | Sharon Au Part 1 欧菁仙 上集
snippet.description:
Currently residing in Paris and having won 4 Best Programme Host in Star Awards, Sharon Au used to made silly mistakes when she first joined the media industry.

When she left the limelight to take on a scholarship to pursue further studies in Japan, little did she expect it would turn out to be yet another legendary and inspirational journey of life.

旅居法国巴黎的欧菁仙，曾经是四届红星大奖最佳主持人，但原来她刚入行时，是不断闯祸和闹笑话。当她放下明星光环，拿奖学金去留学时，没料到又是一段传奇又励志的人生旅程。

Directed & Interviewed by Joe Sabia
Produced by Lily Rhodehamel

snippet.title: HIGHLIGHTS | Arsenal vs Wolves (1-2) | Premier League
snippet.description:
We suffered another damaging defeat at the Emirates, despite scoring our first Premier League goal from open play in six games.
 
The two sides went into the game with identical scoring records - just nine goals conceded and ten conceded each from the opening nine games - but despite that both teams showed plenty of attacking intent in the opening few minutes.
 
But all of that momentum was lost following a horrific looking clash of heads between David Luiz and Raul Jimenez as we attacked a corner. After a stoppage of some 10 minutes, David Luiz was bandaged up and carried on, while Jimenez was stretchered off the pitch.
 
Not surprisingly the game took a while to get going again. The game slowed down and we were punished for a lack of urgency when Wolves took the lead. Leander Dendoncker thumped a header against the bar but Pedro Neto was in the right place to squeeze in the rebound.
 
The goal served to wake us up. Just three minutes later Willian sent in a teasing cross from the right and his compatriot Gabriel rose highest to direct a powerful header past Rui Patricio.
 
The game had opened up and Wolves retook the lead through Daniel Podence. Bernd Leno spilt a deflected shot from Neto and Podence was first to pounce on the loose ball.
 
Rob Holding replaced David Luiz at half-time, who was still clearly feeling the effects of the early collision.
 
We were struggling to put any pace in to our attacks, and also looked vulnerable whenever Wolves broke forward.
 
Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang was receiving limited service, but created a chance for himself when he stole the ball off Patricio's toes outside the area. The keeper scrambled back to push away Aubameyang's low shot however.
 
Substitute Reiss Nelson then shot over when well-placed while Aubameyang headed wide from a deep Bellerin cross.
 
But despite putting the visitors under more pressure in the final 15 minutes, we fell to a third successive league defeat at home.

snippet.title: Kasihan Wani Comel, hanya ‘berlakon’ kurus depan kamera diperdaya usahawan kosmetik
snippet.description:
Menurut Nurul Airawani Nazira Ibrahim atau lebih dikenali sebagai Wani Comel, 23, dia berasa seperti ditipu selepas tidak mendapat apa-apa faedah dan bayaran seperti yang dijanjikan selepas menandatangani kontrak sebagai duta produk. snippet.title: Azwan Ali Gagal Menahan Air Mata, Terkenangkan Persahabatan Dengan Ziana Zain | Lagu Cinta Kita 2
snippet.description:
Siapa yang bakal mengacarakan episod ketiga Lagu Cinta Kita 2? Benarkah Azwan Ali akan kembali bergandingan dengan Elly Mazlein ekoran desakan peminat yang mahukan Diva AA dikekalkan sebagai pengacara? Jika benar, terbuktilah kuasa warganet!

Minggu kedua Lagu Cinta Kita 2 melihat 12 lagi peserta digandingkan sebagai pasangan duet - Ariff & Hidayah, Muhaimin & Kodi, Fariqwan & Mina, Adly Sofwan & Darling, Faez & Sarah dan Iss Arfan & Mya.

Yang berjaya mara ke pusingan seterusnya adalah Ariff & Hidayah, Fariqwan & Mina, Adly Sofwan & Darling serta Iss Arfan & Mya. Namun pasangan yang paling mendapat perhatian penonton adalah Mina & Fariqwan. Persembahan mereka, di mana mereka telah mendendangkan lagu Seiring dan Sejalan berjaya mendapat lebih daripada 110,000 tontonan di YouTube TV3Malaysia (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zYx3NPQgLII).

Bagaimana pula dengan prestasi peserta minggu ini? Nantikan jawapannya Ahad ini di TV3, jam 9 malam. Anda juga boleh strim secara langsung di saluran YouTube TV3Malaysia.

#LaguCintaKita2

snippet.title: 黃鴻升 Alien Huang 【我不是空笑夢 Dream It Real】Official Music Video
snippet.description:
【ROCK HDMV】
歡迎訂閱滾石唱片YouTube官方頻道 → http://bit.ly/RockRecords
#黃鴻升  《#我不是空笑夢》MV

「比起對兒女的愛 那些還沒做過的事 都只是空笑夢」
我們
年少輕狂的時候 希望可以征服全世界
身為子女的我們 帶著年少時的驕傲
有著無限憧憬 希望錯 也要錯得乾脆 
畢竟出發點只有自己 但往往那後座力都是父母在幫我們承擔 
我們可以無負擔地去衝去闖 想證明自己長大 但傷痕累累

父母
年少輕狂的時候 希望可以征服全世界
但 在有了你的那一刻起
一切都不重要了 那～ 那是什麼？
應該是責任吧 
比起對兒女的愛
那些還沒做的事 都只是空笑夢

於是 過了20～30年
才發現自己已不在年輕 一切的希望寄託在子女上
心裏希望我們下一代更茁壯 青出於藍 但又不希望下一代走許多冤枉路，但終究那是他自己的人生 回顧人生這一切 就像一場夢一樣 
就算了失去了夢想 因為有了你 還是充滿笑容
(以上文字介紹由 @黃鴻升 Alien Huang 撰寫於2020/6)

-
你是否也
空 了什麼 
笑 忘什麼
夢 過什麼

對於父母而言  充滿實驗性的事
他們總愛說是   空笑夢

也許吧 
在無法證明想做的不是夢之前
我們僅有的   就是努力 用力去闖

父母其實不是擔心你愛做夢
他們害怕的是  看見你的難過

因爲
人生常常當你覺得ㄧ切美好時
給了你ㄧ場突然如其來的重擊

碰壁了  別忘了 這不是空笑夢
停滯了  放棄了 才會變空笑夢

有個地方   真實的因你而存在
溫暖你  照顧你 讓你安心停下
那個地方就是「家」

-
MV故事是由黃鴻升當初所構思

團隊集結了所有他的能量去完成它
在此由衷感謝所有真心思念他與 ㄧ起完成MV的朋友

黃鴻升的思想不會停止   我們會讓ㄧ切延續下去

「想念  是為了延續精神」

生日快樂！鬼哥！

作詞：隨性_蛋糕

面容上的皺痕
有辛苦 有艱苦 攏無怨無恨
看著你背影的心酸  
為著阮付出青春

你的每一句話 攏是你的體會

這是我的願望   
 
希望你會了解  我毋是咧眠夢

snippet.title: How Grosjean survived fireball Bahrain F1 crash that split his car in two
snippet.description:
Romain Grosjean escaped from one of the scariest F1 crashes in recent memory in the 2020 Bahrain Grand Prix, when his Haas car pierced the barriers and split in half as it caught fire after a 137mph impact. In this video we explain what we know about the crash, how Grosjean climbed out of the wreckage, and the key factors that enabled him to survive an accident that surely would have resulted in a fatality just a few years ago

Taan hi koka peya jadeya ni

Kalla kalla jaanda neyana sadda

Kinna chir rehna udda baabe te depend aa
Jehde time rabb nu aa aake tab dassda
Ni ohi time bande da rakaane hunda end ae

Ni aihde ch rakaane eddi gall ni koyi maan di
Horan naalon likhni ch ehi aa fark
Har bande naal jude gall Bhaini aale Khan di

Ni zindagi de rang dekhe
Duniya de dhang dekhe
Taanhi taan jeyonda jatt neeviyan nu dekh
Hikk tan ke rahi da ban-than ke rahi da
Hon allhadan freeze taur mitran di dekh ke

Ni nature da banda main ajeeb balliye
Dum apne te kitta jo achieve balliye
Ho naam dass ke mili da sadda hass ke mili da
Bass ikko banda dil de kareeb

Sadda Teji naal pyar aa
Ni dilan ch na khar aa
Ni gaaneya ch dass
Kahdi billo jeet haar aa

Ni naa hi kalakaar aa
Ni naa koyi star aa
Ni Bhaini wala balliye
Yaara da bass yaar aa

Ho khud nu jo horan naal karda compare aa ni
Mitran di nazar ch banda oh fail ae
90% aithe negativity aa ni
Main lokkan diyan suna
Mainu enni kithe vail ae

Ho mitran nu farak ni
Chhoti waddi gaddi da
Ni likhan ton pehlan
Ik shaunk si kabaddi da
Ni maari di ni cheekh
Jehda hunda ho jaye leek
Ni main marzi naal likha gaana
Marzi naal chhadi da

Ho Sukh naal babe ne laate rang balliye
Bahle khush ne te 1–2 ne tang balliye
Ho maahde time da zikar ni
Koyi kal di fikar ni
Koyi ajj de samay di munda mangma

Maserati thalle car aa
Ni London ch yaar aa ni
Bahla ni sayana taan hi
Hunda na vyapar aa
Ni karke tarakki struggle ni dassi
Billo lad ke lekhan naal
Hoya gabbru taiyaar ae

snippet.title: The Mandalorian Season 2 Episode 6 Breakdown OH MY GOD
snippet.description:
This episode had it all! The Mandalorian Season 2 Episode 6 finally shows the one and only, Boba Fett in the spotlight. We see Boba return and eventually help Din Djarin and Grogu against Moff Gideon's Storm Troopers and Dark Troopers (phase 2 I think), who end up taking Grogu.
Fennec Shand reminds me a lot of Zam Wessel from Attack of the Clones, who was pursued by Anakin Skywalker and Obi-Wan Kenobi, until Jango showed up.

We also learn a lot about Jango Fett, Boba Fett's Father. We learn that Jango Fett was a Mandalorian! This is awesome! Since it was skewed in canon, it's nice to know we finally have an answer. They seem to be following his story from Open Seasons comic book series which shows the story of Jango as a boy. Long story short, Jango was the son of a farmer on Concord Dawn. A man named Jaster Mereel who was leader of the True Mandalorians, was on the run from a traitor named Tor Vizsla from Death Watch. Jango’s dad hid Jaster Mereel in his farm, and told Jango that he was feeding some homeless men. When Tor Vizsla came looking near Jango’s Dad’s farm, he found Jango’s Dad and beat him up infant of Jango, until Jango’s mom created a distraction and Jango ran for his life, leaving his parents who were immediately murdered, Fett ran into Jaster Mereel who eventually took the boy under his wing and recruited him in the Mandalorian Civil War against Death Watch, as one of the True Mandalorians. Jaster died eventually and Jango avenged him, becoming the leader of the True Mandalorians. Now the people who found Din, were death watch, so the two clans have always been waging wars against one another and have varying beliefs. 

Explaining this to Din, Din accepts that the armour belongs to Boba. So this armour, is just repainted from his dad’s, from Jango’s. The deal is done, says Din, where Boba assures him that it is not, as he promised the safety of the child in return for his armour. Now Boba joins the crew until the child is safe. Flying in the Slave 1, they arrive on Nevarro 7, where Cara Dune is now a New Republic Marshal, where he asks her to locate Mayfeld, who you might remember from season 1. Mando is going to spring him out of jail to locate Moff Gideon’s cruiser.

We jump to Moff Gideon’s light cruiser, he walks to the cell containing the child.

As Moff Gideon enters, we see Grogu using the force on stormtroopers. Even going as far as using force choke, to which many might think is a dark side move, but, I should mention, Luke Skywalker used it as well in Return of the Jedi, and he was far from the dark side.

As Grogu knocks them out, Gideon steps up to him and ignites his 
dark saber, asking Grogu if he remembers one of these, meaning if he remembers using a lightsaber or having seen many lightsabers during his time as a Jedi at the Jedi Temple before Order 66. Grogu is tired, I think because he had to cut himself off from the force for so long that he isn’t used to using it as much as when he was at the Jedi temple learning from the many masters. Using the force can also tire one out, like it does to Luke in the empire strikes back when failing to lift the x-wing out of Yoda’s swamp. They blast Grogu with a stun blast, and cuff him. Gideon tells his officer to contact Dr. Pershing, the cloning doctor responsible for the experiments on the child, to tell him that they have their donor. The plan now is for Gideon to kill Grogu to harvest all of his blood which has force powers, or in Star Wars lingo, a high Midichlorian count. End of the episode.

It was amazing. Simply amazing. My favourite episode of the entire show so far, which is saying a lot. Boba is back and badder than ever, as Terry Silver would say. I think the next episode will revolve around rescuing Mayfeld from Jail, and then tracking the light cruiser or going to Dr. Pershing who will have the child momentarily. I think the season finale will end in a Big Bang all out battle like end game. With everyone we’ve seen from this season fighting together against Moff Gideon and his dark troopers, as he himself gets in a phase 3 dark trooper mega suit to destroy Din. Hopefully Ahsoka Tano returns with Bo Katan, and we get to see another Jedi, Luke or Ezra is my guess.

snippet.title: Solo Female Travellers Incredible Off-Grid Tiny House Truck
snippet.description:
This incredible off-the-grid tiny house truck has been perfectly designed to be a comfortable home on the move! Solar-powered and mounted on the back of a brand new truck, this home is ready to go anywhere! 

Jude made the decision to construct her own tiny house truck after many years of living on the road in campers. Sick of living in other peoples designs and poorly insulated structures which left her cold in the winter, she set about designing her own comfortable tiny house which she mounted on the back of a brand new truck giving her the ability to travel worry free! 

Completely off-the-grid, this home is designed to park up in the most beautiful and remote areas of New Zealand. Designed with comfort in mind, this house truck has all the convenience and comforts of home, all while being ready to travel in a heart-beat. 

In this episode, we tour Jude's amazing tiny house truck, and talk about life as a solo female full time traveller on the road in New Zealand. We hope you enjoy the video! 

Find out more about this tiny house and others on our website: https://www.livingbiginatinyhouse.com/

Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/livingbiginatinyhouse/

Follow us on Facebook:  http://www.facebook.com/livingbiginatinyhouse/

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/tinyhousenz

Please subscribe for more videos on tiny houses, architecture, DIY, design, and sustainable, off-grid living.

60 Minutes, the most successful American television broadcast in history, began its 52nd season in September. Offering hard-hitting investigative reports, interviews, feature segments and profiles of people in the news, the broadcast began in 1968 is still a hit in 2020. 60 Minutes makes Nielsen’s weekly Top 10 nearly every week and was the #1 weekly television broadcast three times last season.


The program still averages more than 10 million viewers, more than double the audience of its nearest network news magazine competitor. The average audience for a 60 Minutes broadcast is 150% higher than those of the network morning news programs; the audience dwarfs the number of viewers drawn by the most popular cable news programs.  


About a million more people listen to the 60 Minutes radio simulcast in several major cities and on its companion podcast. Tens of thousands each week experience 60 Minutes online. The broadcast’s segments can be watched at 60Minutes.com and on the CBS All Access app. Its webcast, 60MinutesOvertime.com, offers content originally produced for the web, including behind-the-scenes video about the production of 60 Minutes stories and timely archival segments.


60 Minutes has won every major broadcast award. Its 25 Peabody and 150 Emmy awards are the most won by any single news program. It has also won 20 duPont-Columbia University journalism awards. Other distinguished journalism honors won multiple times include the George Polk, RTDNA Edward R. Murrow, Investigative Reporters and Editors, RFK Journalism, Sigma Delta Chi and Gerald Loeb awards.

60 Minutes premiered on CBS September 24, 1968. Bill Owens is the program’s executive producer. The correspondents and contributors of 60 Minutes are Sharyn Alfonsi, Anderson Cooper, John Dickerson, Norah O’Donnell, Scott Pelley, Lesley Stahl, Bill Whitaker and L. Jon Wertheim.

snippet.title: Joe Biden's Bizarre Admission & Leaked Teacher's Racism Training | DIRECT MESSAGE | Rubin Report
snippet.description:
Dave Rubin of The Rubin Report discusses the most recent Joe Biden gaffe, possible video evidence of ballot stuffing in Georgia, a leaked white privilege training that turns teachers into activists, and Kitson's in Los Angeles fighting back. First Dave discusses the latest in a line of Biden gaffes or is it an admission of how he plans to leave office to make way for President Harris? Joe Biden also has announced how he would address a mask mandate. In Georgia there appears to be possible voter fraud evidence that was caught on tape. The video allegedly shows suitcases full of ballots that were taken out after counting had stopped for the night. According to Trump’s lawyers this could be enough votes to possibly change the election results. Journalist Christopher Rufo has released a leaked racism and diversity training given to San Diego teachers that he received from a whistleblower. It has all the hallmarks of critical race theory where all the white teachers are lectured about their white privilege and internalized racism. How training teachers in systemic racism will help the area’s low test scores has not been clarified.

snippet.title: DFIDELIZ feat. MC HARIEL - OBRIGADO MÃE, PT.2 (CLIPE OFICIAL)
snippet.description:
Clipe oficial de Dfideliz feat. MC Hariel  - Obrigado Mãe, Pt.2 (prod. LT no Beat & Dj Murillo)

Ouça em todas as plataformas: https://onerpm.lnk.to/ObrigadoMaePt2

- Siga nas redes sociais:

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jazzpraminhaalma
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dfideliz/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/jazzdfideliz

FICHA TÉCNICA:

Interpretes: Dfideliz / Mc Hariel
Composição: Dfideliz / Mc Hariel
Produção: LT no Beat / Dj Murillo
Direção e edição: Bruninho

LETRA:

O mãe, te acho linda de turbante
Me desculpa se eu virei cantor de funk
è nois na porra do bagulho,mas eu tenho
muito orgulho do barulho
O mãe, te acho linda de turbante
Me desculpa se eu virei cantor de funk
è nois na porra do bagulho,mas eu tenho
muito orgulho do barulho
É tipo chover no molhado eu to aqui me declarando
falando pra tu direito o que eu te digo todo dia
mas eu admiro muito que cê fez por mim
o que fizeram com você eu sei que foi mó covardia
mas eu, to ciente que quem bate sempre esquece
quem apanha sempre lembra mas não tem problema não
que eu to contigo e nois se desentende mas é só vida quem dita
a nossa separação, me sinto forte quando você me abraça
canto um ponto forte para a minha proteção
você com seu poder de premonição me avisando dos perigos desse mundão
Como Chico Xavier tua paz me fez pensar como uma mulher o mundo
todo pode enfrentar, que nem uma gladiadora, na guerra em solo inimigo
sua arma era a vassoura
Mas agora eu solto a voz e você nunca mais vai limpar vaso de playboy
O Raoni e o Harine cada vez mais perto de nois a vida só tende a crescer
ouvi a Charles do Futuro até o Fontales Caparroz


Ce quer ver ela puta só ce fala do meu pai! 
Pelo menos ficava, hoje em dia eu nem sei mais 
Minha mãe é das mulher que é independente pá caraio 
Tipo a frase “eu me sustento, nunca precisei de macho” 

Eu lembro que ela me levava pra trampa com ela! 
Fala olha filho o tamanho do casão 
Eu mo pequinininho olhava na cara dela, e falava eu to vendo é igual seu coração 

O mãe quanta história ce carrega nessas perna, fala quantos banheiros essas sua mão lavou 
Ce pode chorar sim, que esse terreno e seu! Fica vontade vai construir o casão que se limpo 

Mais é que hoje é diferente, ce tá mais sorridente 
Eu amo essa risada que agora nem tem mais dente 
O quanto eu te amo ? Eu nem sei o tamanho, meu te juro que isso aqui vai ser nem mais que eternamente 

O meu mãe olha que fita eu to num som com o Hariel, lembra que eu te disse que isso aqui ia virar ?!
Claro que eu te entendia, eu sim te busca, independente da família sim ou não acredita! 

Mas fala mais um pouco, que eu amo sua história 
Na real me pergunto como aguento isso tudo 
Felipe c nunca teve que entender uma mulher, só saiba que sem elas ce não vai dura muito mundo 

Foi lá que eu percebi que ter um pai e uma questão 
Era só assumir, e quando der manda a pensão 
Brigado pela vida, eu juro que eu queria 
Se um dia c partisse, só te dar meu coração

Oh Santa

Santa

Oh, Santa
Oh, Santa

[Refrain]
Oh Santa
Santa gon' come and make him mine this Christmas

Oh Santa

So soon as you leave the North Pole
Santa won't you come and make him mine this Christmas?
 
[Chorus]
Santa's gonna come and make you mine, ho, ho, ho
Santa's gonna come and make you mine this Christmas

snippet.title: Clash Royale: NEW LEGENDARY CARD REVEAL 😮 TV Royale Update
snippet.description:
https://www.youtube.com/esportsroyale
☝️☝️☝️ WATCH THE CLASH ROYALE WORLD FINALS HERE ☝️☝️☝️

It's our first Legendary card since the Fisherman entered the Arena in July 2019! Find out who she is and catch up on what's coming in the next Clash Royale Season... LOGMAS.

Follow Drew & Brice: https://twitter.com/drewbian & https://www.instagram.com/bricelavillesaintmartin_3d/

Subscribe for more! ►► http://supr.cl/SubRoyale

Enter the Arena! From the creators of Clash of Clans comes a real-time multiplayer game starring the Royales, your favorite Clash characters and much, much more.

Collect and upgrade dozens of cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defenses you know and love, as well as the Royales: Princes, Knights, Baby Dragons and more. Knock the enemy King and Princesses from their towers to defeat your opponents and win Trophies, Crowns and glory in the Arena. Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community.

Lead the Clash Royale Family to victory!

FEATURES
• Duel players from around the world in real-time in both 1v1 and 2v2 Battles
• Earn chests to unlock rewards, collect powerful new cards and upgrade existing ones
• Destroy opponent's towers and win Crowns to earn epic Crown chests
• Build and upgrade your card collection with the Clash Royale Family along with dozens of your favorite Clash troops, spells and defenses
• Construct your ultimate Battle Deck to defeat your opponents
• Progress through multiple Arenas all the way to the top
• Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community
• Challenge your Clanmates and friends to a private duel, or play side-by-side in a 2v2 Battle
• Work together with your Clan to unlock Clan Chests
• Play new events every week
• Learn different battle tactics by watching the best duels on TV Royale

PLEASE NOTE! Clash Royale is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash Royale. A network connection is also required.

Support:
Are you having problems? Visit http://supercell.helpshift.com/a/clash-royale/ or contact us in-game by going to Settings, Help and support.

Privacy Policy:
http://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
http://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Parent's Guide:
http://supercell.com/en/parents/

snippet.title: POL1Z1STENS0HN - Bürgermeister | ZDF Magazin Royale
snippet.description:
Nach “Ich hab Polizei”, "BlasserDünnerJunge", "Recht kommt", "herz und faust und zwinker zwinker" beendet POL1Z1STENS0HN, der Five-Track-Superstar,  seine Karriere mit diesem fünften und finalen Track: "Bürgermeister"
Der offizielle Soundtrack Deiner Wahl!

Musik: Score Squad (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCExV9Hl1Q4AAiwRmLnnfLPw)

Lyrics:
alle hände nach oben! wer ist erste gewalt?
hat mit kette und sein benz (von vater staat bezahlt)
hure legislatur an tag 1 direkt auf strich gebracht?
fahrersitz, schleudersitz, katapult an die macht! 

ich bin bürgermeister jetzt! ich bin das gesetz!
exekutier legislativ wenn du mein recht verletzt! 
mach platz! bürgermeister kommt! aus dem weg! 
ihr seid unten, ich bin oben! autorität! 

machiavelli theorie – bürgermeister praxis,
deine lobby will mein arsch? gib ersma bakschisch! 
du willst bürgermeister sein? das will jeder!
ich spiel schach mit baseballschläger!

cops tanzen hier nach meiner rattenfängerpfeife!
staatsanwalt bückt sich nach meiner bürgermeisterseife!
ihr seid nur sicher, wenn ich bürgermeister bin! 
ihr wollt meine lyrics? ich will eure stimmen!

Steh auf! Bürgermeister! Auf! Auf! Bürgermeister!

alle hände nach oben! wer ist erste gewalt?
wer repräsentiert, kontrolliert, wer regiert?  
ich bin bürgermeister, mama! ich mach das gesetz!
zerleg  souverän mit flex GERMANIAS LEX!

infratest diesdas, meine mehrheit fickt 
dich yarak, absolut! bricht dein wendehals genick!
dropkick von unten – kampfkandidatur!
bella ciao, bist von gestern wie humor von dieter nuhr!

hardcore oldschool norm zerbohrn!
wir sterben dafür, denn dafür  sind dafür geboren!
sonne geht auf, wenn ich bürgermeister bin! 
ich brauche eure lyrics und leih euch meine stimme! 

und alle cops tanzen dann nach unserer pfeife!
und staatsanwalt bückt sich dann nach unserer seife!

alle hände nach oben! wer ist erste gewalt!
hat die kette und den benz und vater staat bezahlt?
kein heititei gelaber! greift wehrhaft an! 
mighty legislative – die alles und die jeder kann!

wir killen abschaum im ausschuss mit unseren kompromissen
in zehn stunden sitzungen ohne zu pissen

kein heititei gelaber! greift wehrhaft an! 
mighty legislative – die alles und die jeder kann!

wir killen abschaum im ausschuss mit unseren kompromissen
in zehn stunden sitzungen ohne zu pissen
wenn keiner macht hat keiner macht!
und das letzte was du bastard sehen wirst, ist wer zuletzt lacht!

tu quoque, hurensohn, fili mi!
knips dein scheiß playback aus – wie milli vanilli
zerbeißen al dente scheißargumente – radikal demokrat!
wer ist bürgermeister meister? wer ist der staat?

auf! auf sagt es allen! wir sind frei! 
und unser recht kommt! und wir haben polizei! 
ihr sagt der blasse junge gehört in therapie
kann sein, doch um mich weht ein hauch von 

anarchie! demokratie! anarchie! demokratie!

Heute könntet ihr ein DYSON AIRWRAP gewinnen! 🎁
🎄BROZEMBER ADVENTSKALENDER VERLOSUNG
.
Wie könnt ihr teilnehmen:
1. @dashaus auf Instagram Folgen!
2. @crispyrob @dimakoslowski @falcofalcrow @selfiesandra und @moritzmeter auf Instagram Folgen!
3. Einen Kommentar unter diesem Post schreiben!
(Ihr könnte so viele Kommentare schreiben wie ihr wollt, um eure Gewinnchancen zu steigern, der Preis wird unter allen Kommentaren zufällig verlost)
.
Viel Glück, Freunde ❤️
.
Die Gewinner werden per DM kontaktiert und ihr Kommentar wird im nächsten Brozember Video eingeblendet.
Die Gewinner haben 7 Tage Zeit um auf die DM zu antworten, danach kann der Preis an einen anderen Teilnehmer verlost werden.
Die Teilnahmebedingungen sind in der Instagram-Bio verlinkt.
Instagram: http://instagram.com/selfiesandra
Podcast: http://dickunddoof.lnk.to/_pHBV

snippet.description:

NWG Kids auf YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCl83fqA0Xf7W-yobct7ZE8A

Zweite Finalrunde der 5. und Jubiläumsstaffel: Nur die Athleten, die in der ersten Finalshow nach allen neun Hindernissen innerhalb der vorgegebenen Zeit von 4:30 Minuten gebuzzert haben, sind in der zweiten Finalrunde mit dabei. Wer wird es sein? Sind die Favoriten der Moderatoren Frank Buschmann, Jan Köppen und Laura Wontorra mit dabei? Am Ende steht der Mount Midoriyama, der diesmal unter freiem Himmel in Köln auf seine Eroberer wartet. Zweite Finalrunde der 5. und Jubiläumsstaffel: Nur die Athleten, die in der ersten Finalshow nach allen neun Hindernissen innerhalb der vorgegebenen Zeit von 4:30 Minuten gebuzzert haben, sind heute in der zweiten Finalrunde mit dabei. Wer wird es sein? Sind die Favoriten der Moderatoren Frank Buschmann, Jan Köppen und Laura Wontorra mit dabei?

Die Athleten im zweiten Teil des Finales erwarten folgende Hindernisse: In Runde 2 (auf Zeit) die Chaos-Kegel (neu), die Schwingflügel, die Zickzack-Himmelsleiter, die Steuerräder und die vertikalen Hebebrücken (neu). Nach kurzer Pause geht's weiter in Runde 3 (ohne Zeitvorgabe) mit den schwebenden Türen, dem Spaziergang, über die Finger-Leisten 3.0 zu den Steck-Kästen und den Kugel-Haken bis zum Stangen-Flug. Am Ende steht der Mount Midoriyama, der diesmal unter freiem Himmel in Köln auf seine Eroberer wartet. Wer wird vor dem finalen Hindernis stehen, und schafft es ein Athlet in diesem Jahr endlich, den Mount zu bezwingen?

snippet.title: Clash Royale: NEW LEGENDARY CARD REVEAL 😮 TV Royale Update
snippet.description:
https://www.youtube.com/esportsroyale
☝️☝️☝️ WATCH THE CLASH ROYALE WORLD FINALS HERE ☝️☝️☝️

It's our first Legendary card since the Fisherman entered the Arena in July 2019! Find out who she is and catch up on what's coming in the next Clash Royale Season... LOGMAS.

Follow Drew & Brice: https://twitter.com/drewbian & https://www.instagram.com/bricelavillesaintmartin_3d/

Subscribe for more! ►► http://supr.cl/SubRoyale

Enter the Arena! From the creators of Clash of Clans comes a real-time multiplayer game starring the Royales, your favorite Clash characters and much, much more.

Collect and upgrade dozens of cards featuring the Clash of Clans troops, spells and defenses you know and love, as well as the Royales: Princes, Knights, Baby Dragons and more. Knock the enemy King and Princesses from their towers to defeat your opponents and win Trophies, Crowns and glory in the Arena. Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community.

Lead the Clash Royale Family to victory!

FEATURES
• Duel players from around the world in real-time in both 1v1 and 2v2 Battles
• Earn chests to unlock rewards, collect powerful new cards and upgrade existing ones
• Destroy opponent's towers and win Crowns to earn epic Crown chests
• Build and upgrade your card collection with the Clash Royale Family along with dozens of your favorite Clash troops, spells and defenses
• Construct your ultimate Battle Deck to defeat your opponents
• Progress through multiple Arenas all the way to the top
• Form a Clan to share cards and build your very own battle community
• Challenge your Clanmates and friends to a private duel, or play side-by-side in a 2v2 Battle
• Work together with your Clan to unlock Clan Chests
• Play new events every week
• Learn different battle tactics by watching the best duels on TV Royale

PLEASE NOTE! Clash Royale is free to download and play, however, some game items can also be purchased for real money. If you don't want to use this feature, please disable in-app purchases in your device's settings. Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash Royale. A network connection is also required.

Support:
Are you having problems? Visit http://supercell.helpshift.com/a/clash-royale/ or contact us in-game by going to Settings, Help and support.

Privacy Policy:
http://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
http://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

Parent's Guide:
http://supercell.com/en/parents/

LYRICS
Kann nicht mehr schlafen, 
bin seit Tagen wach
Halt kaum aus, wie sehr ich dich und mich verraten hab

doch ich kann das nicht 
Was du bedeutest, weiß ich erst,
seit du gegangen bist

wärst du vielleicht noch bei mir 
Hab nur an mich gedacht zu oft
Verzeih mir

Ich trag schwarz, 
bis es was Dunkleres gibt
Hab dir zu spät gesagt,
was du für mich bist, ja 
Hätt nicht gedacht,
wie schwer es ohne dich ist 
Werd nie mehr jemanden so lieben wie dich

Ich trag schwarz,
bis es was Dunkleres gibt
Frag mich die ganze Zeit,
wo du grade bist, ja 
Hätt nicht gedacht,
wie schwer es ohne dich ist 
Werd nie mehr jemanden so lieben wie dich 

Ich kann’s nicht glauben,
dass es zu Ende ist 
Dass du nie wieder mit nem Rotwein an meinem Fenster sitzt

Wollt immer streiten, 
hab es nicht gerafft
Hab dich so verletzt,
bis du’s nicht mehr ertragen hast

Ich weiß, ich hab es nicht verdient,
dass du mir noch ne Chance gibst
Denn manche Wunden sind zu tief
So tief

snippet.title: CRO - Hoch (Official Video)
snippet.description:
'Hoch' überall streamen: https://umg.lnk.to/HOCH

Check CRO im Netz:
► Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/cromusic
► Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/thisiscro 
► Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/thisiscro

Lyrics:
 
Sag mir wie weit über dem Boden fängt der Himmel an
Als wir kleiner waren kamen wir immer ran
Nur einmal nicht kurz aufgepasst, ist der Traum geplatzt 
Und du bist aufgewacht
Und jetzt füllst du diese Leere, so als ob nichts wäre
Nimmst irgendetwas gegen die Schwere
Denn es gibt so vieles was dich runterzieht
In einer Welt voller Gravitation macht deine Leichtigkeit den Unterschied
Ich schreib dir einen Brief
Doch ich schick ihn nicht ab
Es gibt so vieles was ein Wort niemals sagt
Man fährt die Liebe in einem schicken Wagen an die Wand und merkt es nicht
Was für ein beschissenes Geräusch, wenn ein Herz bricht
Doch manchmal geht es einfach so
Alles holt dich down, lass es einfach los
Die Dinge unter dir, die sind gar nicht mehr so groß
Schau nach oben und auf einmal geht’s hoch
 
Choir
Es geht hoch
Hoch (3x)
Es geht hoch
Hoch (3x)
 
Es geht hoch, ich halt mich fest, ich bin nicht schwindelfrei
Doch egal was kommt, ich bin dabei
Denn es geht nicht darum was geht, sondern darum was für immer bleibt
Wieso sieht man Dinge nie kommen doch immer gehen
Manches sieht man einmal, es wird für immer fehlen
Hunderttausend Likes, doch ich fühl mich allein
Ich sag die Wahrheit, weil sich Lügen nicht reimt
Ich liebe es zu lieben und ich hasse es zu hassen
Vom Geld habe ich genug, lass uns alles verprassen
Die meisten haben Angst vor der Angst
Ist ein Tanz auf Distanz
Komm nicht ran und kann es einfach nicht fassen
Wollen Erfolg, Sie folgen, Wir folgen
Alle blind
Ich mach die Augen auf und folge nur noch dem Wind
Wirf den Ballast ab, alles wird leichter, einfach so
Wir heben ab, schnall dich an, wir heben ab, es geht hoch
 
Choir
Es geht hoch
Hoch (3x)
Es geht hoch
Hoch (3x)
 
Und ich bleib, bleib, bleib bei mir
Ich bleib bei mir

Direction:  truworks 
Kamera: Juhanisaeglep, Oli Maitland, Elton Anderson 
Edit: Oli Maitland
Grading: Oscar Fernandez

snippet.title: Südalpen vor Schneechaos (04.12.2020)
snippet.description:
In den Alpen drohen übers Wochenende gewaltige Schneefälle. Vor allem in den Südalpen kommen dabei 1 bis 2 Meter Neuschnee zusammen. Örtlich sind sogar extreme Mengen von mehr als 3 Meter möglich. Wir verfolgen wie sich die Lage zuspitzt.

snippet.title: Lohnunternehmen in Tirol 🚜☀️🏔️ Hackgut Schernthaner | Arbeiten wo andere Urlaub machen
snippet.description:
Rundballen pressen in Heu und Silage, in der Ebene und am Hang. Maschinen Einsätze in anspruchsvollem Gelände. Arbeiten wo andere Urlaub machen, in einer atemberaubenden Landschaft. Gülle ausbringen mit etwas anderer Technik. Hackguterzeugung und Transport und natürlich die Pflege und Wartung des Fuhrparks: So könnte man den Alltag von Lohnunternehmer Andreas Schernthaner aus Tirol in wenigen Sätzen beschreiben. Den ganzen Sommer über haben wir ihn und sein Team bei ihrer Arbeit immer wieder mit der Kamera begleitet.

Das Hauptstandbein ist die Hackschnitzel Erzeugung und der Hackgut Handel. Hier setzt Schernthaner auf einen Zapfwellen Hacker von Eschlböck, den Biber 83 mit einer Krankabine von Epsilon. Als Zugpferd spannt der Lonunternehmer einen John Deere 7310R vor. Den Transport übernehmen ebenfalls John Deere Traktoren, ein John Deere 6155R und ein John Deere 6210R mit großen Muldenkippern von Schweighofer und Krampe. Eine neue Dienstleistung ist das Rundballen pressen. Hier kommt eine John Deere C441R Press Wickel Kombi zum Einsatz. Für die Arbeit in Hanglagen verwendet Schernthaner einen Lindner Geotrac 94 mit Zwillingsrädern und einer Krone Bellima Rundballenpresse. Auf ein 16 Kubikmeter Bauer Güllefass mit Hochdruck wurde dieses Jahr angeschafft. Damit bringt der Lohnunternehmer die Gülle vom Tal auf die Almen am Berg und düngt dort die Steilflächen.

localizations.de.title: Lohnunternehmen in Tirol 🚜☀️🏔️ Hackgut Schernthaner | Arbeiten wo andere Urlaub machen
localizations.de.description:
Rundballen pressen in Heu und Silage, in der Ebene und am Hang. Maschinen Einsätze in anspruchsvollem Gelände. Arbeiten wo andere Urlaub machen, in einer atemberaubenden Landschaft. Gülle ausbringen mit etwas anderer Technik. Hackguterzeugung und Transport und natürlich die Pflege und Wartung des Fuhrparks: So könnte man den Alltag von Lohnunternehmer Andreas Schernthaner aus Tirol in wenigen Sätzen beschreiben. Den ganzen Sommer über haben wir ihn und sein Team bei ihrer Arbeit immer wieder mit der Kamera begleitet.

Das Hauptstandbein ist die Hackschnitzel Erzeugung und der Hackgut Handel. Hier setzt Schernthaner auf einen Zapfwellen Hacker von Eschlböck, den Biber 83 mit einer Krankabine von Epsilon. Als Zugpferd spannt der Lonunternehmer einen John Deere 7310R vor. Den Transport übernehmen ebenfalls John Deere Traktoren, ein John Deere 6155R und ein John Deere 6210R mit großen Muldenkippern von Schweighofer und Krampe. Eine neue Dienstleistung ist das Rundballen pressen. Hier kommt eine John Deere C441R Press Wickel Kombi zum Einsatz. Für die Arbeit in Hanglagen verwendet Schernthaner einen Lindner Geotrac 94 mit Zwillingsrädern und einer Krone Bellima Rundballenpresse. Auf ein 16 Kubikmeter Bauer Güllefass mit Hochdruck wurde dieses Jahr angeschafft. Damit bringt der Lohnunternehmer die Gülle vom Tal auf die Almen am Berg und düngt dort die Steilflächen.

Inhalt des Videos:

0:51 Auf dem Weg zum ersten Einsatz

7:35 Mitarbeiter Martin Scharnagl
8:42 John Deere C441R Press Wickel Kombination
11:32 Rundballen pressen am Hang
14:01 Gülle fahren mit Hochdruck Düse
15:37 Stammholz hacken im Heizwerk Söll
16:20 Ersatzteil Lieferung vom Lagerhaus
16:55 Zukunftspläne
17:27 Abschluss

snippet.title: Kims Schwangerschafts-Gedanken! | Berlin - Tag & Nacht #2337
snippet.description:
Kim weiß nicht, was sie tun soll! Das Kind behalten oder abtreiben?! Sie führt viele Gespräche – auch mit Mike! Er möchte auf jeden Fall nicht, dass Kim abtreibt! Er würde gerne nochmal Papa werden! Kim muss nochmal nachdenken, was sie wirklich möchte! Sie ist total verwirrt! 

Die gescriptete Reality-Soap „Berlin - Tag & Nacht“ zeigt die coolste WG Berlins, mit Themen wie  Freundschaft, Liebe,  Eifersucht, Affären, Glück, Freude und Leiden. Wie im echten Leben eben!
Alte wie neue WG-Bewohner, u. a. Ole, Joe, Peggy, Krätze, Schmidti, Eule, Basti Paula, Piet, Milla, Leon und viele weitere, zeigen dir ihr Leben in Berlin, der bunten Metropole Deutschlands. Sie nehmen dich mit in ihre Wohngemeinschaften, auf ihre Arbeitsplätze, in den Club Matrix, den Friseursalon „Schnitte“ sowie die Bar LA 14. Auch ein Tattoostudio und das Fitnessstudio Body Burn gehören zu den unterschiedlichen und wechselnden Handlungsorten der Serie. Die Großstadt-Soap „Berlin – Tag & Nacht“ ist nicht zuletzt deshalb so beliebt, weil sie die Bewohner der WGs im Ringen mit alltäglichen Problemen zeigt: Affäre und Eifersucht, Erfolgsdruck im Beruf sowie viele zwischenmenschliche Konflikte. 

"Berlin - Tag & Nacht" läuft Montag bis Freitag um 19:05 Uhr bei RTLZWEI.

snippet.title: Endlich! Willi und Jasmin Herren haben sich wieder | Temptation Island V.I.P. - Folge 09
snippet.description:
Jetzt streamen: https://www.tvnow.de/shows/temptation-island-vip-19095?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=editorial&utm_campaign=beschreibung&utm_term=tvnow   
Alle Infos: https://www.rtl.de/sendungen/real-life/temptation-island/?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=editorial&utm_campaign=beschreibung&utm_term=tvnow

Hach, endlich ist es so weit. Nach langen Wochen der Sehnsucht dürfen sich Willi und Jasmin Herren endlich wieder in den Armen liegen. Eine Zeit, in der sich Willi mehr als einmal wegen seiner Liebsten den Kopf zerbrochen hat. Wieso hatte sie sich über seine Nutella-Fressattacken bei den anderen lustig gemacht? Und was ist es, was er keinesfalls gezeigt bekommen sollte? Als Willi diese Aussage seiner Jasmin beim Einzellagerfeuer sah, war der Schlagerstar dem Zusammenbruch nah. "Das ist unfair!", hatte er unter Tränen geschimpft. Wie er jetzt reagiert, als Jasmin alle Unklarheiten beseitigt und die beiden sich endlich wieder haben, zeigt das Video.

Doch vor dem schönen Wiedersehen wurden Willi und Jasmin ein letztes Mal auf die Probe gestellt. Beim romantischen Temptation-Date mit einer der heißen Verführerinnen und einem der heißen Verführer wurde ihre Treue ein letztes Mal auf die Probe gestellt. Willi genoss bei einer Trüffelsuche einen schönen Tag mit Maria. Und die gefunden Trüffel durften dann ganz frisch beim Candlelight-Dinner verspeist werden. 

Auch Jasmins Treue soll beim letzten Temptation-Date mit einem heißen Verführer ein letztes Mal auf die Probe gestellt werden. Doch statt sich auf den romantischen Abend mit dem Single-Mann zu konzentrieren, kann sie nur an Willi denken. "Wir bleiben erstmal drei Tage im Bett", schwärmt sie beim Gedanken an ihren Liebsten.

Doch nicht nur Willi und Jasmin, auch die anderen drei Promi-Paare treffen sich endlich wieder. Wie das ausgeht, gibt's schon jetzt und nächste Woche Donnerstag, den 10.12. bei "Temptation Island VIP" auf TVNOW zu sehen.

snippet.title: The Mandalorian Season 2 Episode 6 Breakdown OH MY GOD
snippet.description:
This episode had it all! The Mandalorian Season 2 Episode 6 finally shows the one and only, Boba Fett in the spotlight. We see Boba return and eventually help Din Djarin and Grogu against Moff Gideon's Storm Troopers and Dark Troopers (phase 2 I think), who end up taking Grogu.
Fennec Shand reminds me a lot of Zam Wessel from Attack of the Clones, who was pursued by Anakin Skywalker and Obi-Wan Kenobi, until Jango showed up.

We also learn a lot about Jango Fett, Boba Fett's Father. We learn that Jango Fett was a Mandalorian! This is awesome! Since it was skewed in canon, it's nice to know we finally have an answer. They seem to be following his story from Open Seasons comic book series which shows the story of Jango as a boy. Long story short, Jango was the son of a farmer on Concord Dawn. A man named Jaster Mereel who was leader of the True Mandalorians, was on the run from a traitor named Tor Vizsla from Death Watch. Jango’s dad hid Jaster Mereel in his farm, and told Jango that he was feeding some homeless men. When Tor Vizsla came looking near Jango’s Dad’s farm, he found Jango’s Dad and beat him up infant of Jango, until Jango’s mom created a distraction and Jango ran for his life, leaving his parents who were immediately murdered, Fett ran into Jaster Mereel who eventually took the boy under his wing and recruited him in the Mandalorian Civil War against Death Watch, as one of the True Mandalorians. Jaster died eventually and Jango avenged him, becoming the leader of the True Mandalorians. Now the people who found Din, were death watch, so the two clans have always been waging wars against one another and have varying beliefs. 

Explaining this to Din, Din accepts that the armour belongs to Boba. So this armour, is just repainted from his dad’s, from Jango’s. The deal is done, says Din, where Boba assures him that it is not, as he promised the safety of the child in return for his armour. Now Boba joins the crew until the child is safe. Flying in the Slave 1, they arrive on Nevarro 7, where Cara Dune is now a New Republic Marshal, where he asks her to locate Mayfeld, who you might remember from season 1. Mando is going to spring him out of jail to locate Moff Gideon’s cruiser.

We jump to Moff Gideon’s light cruiser, he walks to the cell containing the child.

As Moff Gideon enters, we see Grogu using the force on stormtroopers. Even going as far as using force choke, to which many might think is a dark side move, but, I should mention, Luke Skywalker used it as well in Return of the Jedi, and he was far from the dark side.

As Grogu knocks them out, Gideon steps up to him and ignites his 
dark saber, asking Grogu if he remembers one of these, meaning if he remembers using a lightsaber or having seen many lightsabers during his time as a Jedi at the Jedi Temple before Order 66. Grogu is tired, I think because he had to cut himself off from the force for so long that he isn’t used to using it as much as when he was at the Jedi temple learning from the many masters. Using the force can also tire one out, like it does to Luke in the empire strikes back when failing to lift the x-wing out of Yoda’s swamp. They blast Grogu with a stun blast, and cuff him. Gideon tells his officer to contact Dr. Pershing, the cloning doctor responsible for the experiments on the child, to tell him that they have their donor. The plan now is for Gideon to kill Grogu to harvest all of his blood which has force powers, or in Star Wars lingo, a high Midichlorian count. End of the episode.

It was amazing. Simply amazing. My favourite episode of the entire show so far, which is saying a lot. Boba is back and badder than ever, as Terry Silver would say. I think the next episode will revolve around rescuing Mayfeld from Jail, and then tracking the light cruiser or going to Dr. Pershing who will have the child momentarily. I think the season finale will end in a Big Bang all out battle like end game. With everyone we’ve seen from this season fighting together against Moff Gideon and his dark troopers, as he himself gets in a phase 3 dark trooper mega suit to destroy Din. Hopefully Ahsoka Tano returns with Bo Katan, and we get to see another Jedi, Luke or Ezra is my guess.

localizations.en.title: The Mandalorian Season 2 Episode 6 Breakdown OH MY GOD
localizations.en.description:
This episode had it all! The Mandalorian Season 2 Episode 6 finally shows the one and only, Boba Fett in the spotlight. We see Boba return and eventually help Din Djarin and Grogu against Moff Gideon's Storm Troopers and Dark Troopers (phase 2 I think), who end up taking Grogu.
Fennec Shand reminds me a lot of Zam Wessel from Attack of the Clones, who was pursued by Anakin Skywalker and Obi-Wan Kenobi, until Jango showed up.

We also learn a lot about Jango Fett, Boba Fett's Father. We learn that Jango Fett was a Mandalorian! This is awesome! Since it was skewed in canon, it's nice to know we finally have an answer. They seem to be following his story from Open Seasons comic book series which shows the story of Jango as a boy. Long story short, Jango was the son of a farmer on Concord Dawn. A man named Jaster Mereel who was leader of the True Mandalorians, was on the run from a traitor named Tor Vizsla from Death Watch. Jango’s dad hid Jaster Mereel in his farm, and told Jango that he was feeding some homeless men. When Tor Vizsla came looking near Jango’s Dad’s farm, he found Jango’s Dad and beat him up infant of Jango, until Jango’s mom created a distraction and Jango ran for his life, leaving his parents who were immediately murdered, Fett ran into Jaster Mereel who eventually took the boy under his wing and recruited him in the Mandalorian Civil War against Death Watch, as one of the True Mandalorians. Jaster died eventually and Jango avenged him, becoming the leader of the True Mandalorians. Now the people who found Din, were death watch, so the two clans have always been waging wars against one another and have varying beliefs. 

Explaining this to Din, Din accepts that the armour belongs to Boba. So this armour, is just repainted from his dad’s, from Jango’s. The deal is done, says Din, where Boba assures him that it is not, as he promised the safety of the child in return for his armour. Now Boba joins the crew until the child is safe. Flying in the Slave 1, they arrive on Nevarro 7, where Cara Dune is now a New Republic Marshal, where he asks her to locate Mayfeld, who you might remember from season 1. Mando is going to spring him out of jail to locate Moff Gideon’s cruiser.

We jump to Moff Gideon’s light cruiser, he walks to the cell containing the child.

As Moff Gideon enters, we see Grogu using the force on stormtroopers. Even going as far as using force choke, to which many might think is a dark side move, but, I should mention, Luke Skywalker used it as well in Return of the Jedi, and he was far from the dark side.

As Grogu knocks them out, Gideon steps up to him and ignites his 
dark saber, asking Grogu if he remembers one of these, meaning if he remembers using a lightsaber or having seen many lightsabers during his time as a Jedi at the Jedi Temple before Order 66. Grogu is tired, I think because he had to cut himself off from the force for so long that he isn’t used to using it as much as when he was at the Jedi temple learning from the many masters. Using the force can also tire one out, like it does to Luke in the empire strikes back when failing to lift the x-wing out of Yoda’s swamp. They blast Grogu with a stun blast, and cuff him. Gideon tells his officer to contact Dr. Pershing, the cloning doctor responsible for the experiments on the child, to tell him that they have their donor. The plan now is for Gideon to kill Grogu to harvest all of his blood which has force powers, or in Star Wars lingo, a high Midichlorian count. End of the episode.

It was amazing. Simply amazing. My favourite episode of the entire show so far, which is saying a lot. Boba is back and badder than ever, as Terry Silver would say. I think the next episode will revolve around rescuing Mayfeld from Jail, and then tracking the light cruiser or going to Dr. Pershing who will have the child momentarily. I think the season finale will end in a Big Bang all out battle like end game. With everyone we’ve seen from this season fighting together against Moff Gideon and his dark troopers, as he himself gets in a phase 3 dark trooper mega suit to destroy Din. Hopefully Ahsoka Tano returns with Bo Katan, and we get to see another Jedi, Luke or Ezra is my guess.

snippet.title: Challenge: Fäll einen Baum und triff damit ein Ziel || Das schaffst du nie!
snippet.description:
Ari muss mit einer Axt einen über 20 Meter hohen Baum fällen! Ihr sagt, dass das für die Maschine keine Challenge ist? Stimmt! Deshalb macht Fiesling Marc es noch einen Tick schwerer: der Baum muss in einen nur rund drei Meter breiten Korridor fallen! Der Waldbesitzer sagt: das ist fast unmöglich. Ob Ari das trotzdem hinbekommt, seht ihr in der neuen Folge von „Das schaffst du nie!“. 
 
1000 BÄUME GEPFLANZT – GEFÄLLT 1 BAUM 

Erinnert ihr euch noch an die „Rettet den Regenwald“-Challenge? Da ging es darum 1.000 Bäume im indoneischen Regenwald zu pflanzen. Dieses Mal geht es um einen Wald in Bayern. Hier muss ein Baum weichen, damit wieder Platz ist für neue Setzlinge: und zwar für Fichten. Das soll den Wald verjüngen. Ari hilft also der Natur bei der Verjüngungskur. Schafft sie es, ohne Anweisung den Baum zu fällen? 

MARC FÖRSTER – DER KING DER WORTSPIELE 

Schlechte Witze sind der zweite Vorname von unserem Fiesling Marc Seibold. Doch heute werden nicht nur die allerfeinsten schlechten Witze serviert, sondern auch noch die schlechtesten Wortspiele! Marc Förster, nicht zu verwechseln mit Mark Forster, ist der König der Wortspiele! Schreibt doch in die Kommentare, welches das schlechteste Wortspiel von Marc in diesem Video war. 

#funk #dsdn #dasschaffstdunie 

******************************************************************** 

Ob 72h moderieren, eine Skischanze hochrennen oder eine Skulptur aus Eis schnitzen: Bei „Das schaffst du nie!“ stellt der fiese Redakteur Marc Seibold den zwei Hosts Ariane Alter und Sebastian Meinberg immer abwechselnd eine Challenge – gerne auch 24 Stunden lang. Schaffen die Hosts die Challenge, dürfen sie Marc bestrafen. Schaffen sie es nicht, müssen sie noch eine Bestrafung ertragen. Jeden Donnerstag um 15 Uhr gibt’s ein neues Video von „Das schaffst du nie!“. Heute: Fälle einen Baum. Auf jede neue Challenge kommt am darauffolgenden Donnerstag die Bestrafung.
